1. Introduction
This is a python interface of OpenDaylight Northband REST API. It contains most of APIs except OpenStack's OpenDaylight management APIs.

2. Dependcies
This software uses requests for HTTP connection. You can install it using pip tools just like:
pip install requests

3. Usage
test-API.py is a sample of how to use this software.

4. Bugs and Problems
This software still needs much test.

5. To Do
High-level APIs based on REST APIs is under developing.
OpenStack's OpenDaylight management will be added soon.

